Package: MF.beta4
Type: Package
Title: Measuring ecosystem multifunctionality and assessing BEF relationships
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anne Chao, Chun-Yu Liu, K. H. Hu
Maintainer: Anne Chao <chao@stat.nthu.edu.tw>
Description: Provide simple functions to (i) compute a class of multifunctionality
      measures for a single ecosystem for given function weights, (ii) decompose gamma
      multifunctionality for multiple ecosystems into a within-ecosystem component (alpha
      multifunctionality) and an among-ecosystem component (beta multifunctionality). In
      each case, the correlation between functions can be corrected for. Based on
      biodiversity and ecosystem function data, this software also facilitates graphics
      for assessing biodiversity-ecosystem functioning (BEF) relationships across 
      scales. 
License: GPL (>= 3)
